==Participating nations==
A total of twenty-eight nations from the [[Allies of World War I]] were invited to the competition and eighteen nations accepted the invite. China aimed to compete, but ultimately was unable to send any athletes to the games within the time scale. It did, however, provide medals and trophies in support of the games. The [[Kingdom of Hejaz]] sent a delegation but with no athletes, choosing to demonstrate the skills of their Arabian horsemen instead. A full list of participants was made by the organisers.
